<br>
Buffs are NOT Free.  Aside from the material components which some buffs require (I know Spirit of the Wolf isn't one that does use a material component), all buffs require mana, which requires time.  That time could have been spent killing something and looting it.  If the caster already had her eight slots full with other spells, then it will also take additional time to sit down and memorize the buff, then after casting it, sit down again to forget it and re-memorize the spell that was in that spell slot originally.<br>
<br>
The LEAST you can do is acknowledge that someone is giving you something that does cost them when they cast a buff on you.<br>
<br>
<br>
